WEBVTT

00:00:00.653 --> 00:00:02.751
-haltn bay kasete numer dray

00:00:02.751 --> 00:00:04.410
bite dertseyln zi vayter.

00:00:04.635 --> 00:00:05.878
yetst iz azoy

00:00:06.323 --> 00:00:08.629
dos iz geven fir un fertsiker yor

00:00:08.128 --> 00:00:10.181
yo, zumer fir un fertsik

00:00:09.310 --> 00:00:11.019
yo, iz arayn der rus

00:00:11.019 --> 00:00:13.210
un ikh hob nokh alts gevoynt bay der goye

00:00:13.210 --> 00:00:15.310
vos zi iz geven azoy vi mayns a mame

00:00:15.310 --> 00:00:18.780
nor vos iz? eyn zakh bet ikh antshuldikung vos ikh hob nisht dertseylt.

00:00:18.507 --> 00:00:19.378
bite

00:00:18.878 --> 00:00:20.560
fun der goye hob ikh nisht dertseylt

00:00:19.688 --> 00:00:20.694
bite

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:22.061
KATERINA ⟨YATSEKHOVA⟩.

00:00:21.561 --> 00:00:22.449
yo

00:00:22.742 --> 00:00:24.676
zi hot di gantse tsayt

00:00:24.868 --> 00:00:27.936
mir gezogt az zi ken mir nisht haltn

00:00:27.936 --> 00:00:28.828
on a

00:00:28.868 --> 00:00:30.550
oysshray- on a meldung

00:00:30.319 --> 00:00:32.619
dos hot ir, dos hot ir yo gezogt. yo.

00:00:30.550 --> 00:00:32.070
ikh zol forn in mayn

00:00:32.070 --> 00:00:33.140
kh'hob yo gezogt?

00:00:32.619 --> 00:00:33.334
yo.

00:00:33.140 --> 00:00:34.690
vi ikh hob ir dertseylt a yidishe?

00:00:34.015 --> 00:00:36.500
yo, yo, dos hot ir shoyn dertseylt. yo.

00:00:35.210 --> 00:00:36.630
dos hob ikh yo? ah, SLICHA.

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:38.277
d- dos hot ir dertseylt.

00:00:36.630 --> 00:00:37.810
bet ikh SLICHA.

00:00:37.810 --> 00:00:40.196
iz geyen mir yetst, ikh hob gemeynt az ikh hob dos nisht gezogt.

00:00:39.162 --> 00:00:41.096
geyen mir foroys, bite.

00:00:40.196 --> 00:00:41.445
geyen mir foroys.

00:00:41.445 --> 00:00:44.488
der rus kumt arayn in fir un fertsikstn yor.

00:00:44.865 --> 00:00:48.625
s'iz do zeyer a sakh gehargete lebn undzer shtub vos me geyt

00:00:48.625 --> 00:00:51.153
un ikh frey zikh shoyn az ikh hob ibergelebt

00:00:51.598 --> 00:00:53.988
un se vert a yidishe komitet

00:00:54.366 --> 00:00:57.296
un ikh heyb on tsu kumen in dem yidishn komitet

00:00:57.437 --> 00:00:59.518
un dort kumen zeyer yidn

00:00:59.518 --> 00:01:02.324
da- oysgedarte fun di kelers

00:01:02.517 --> 00:01:04.924
un se kumt eyne a froy mit a kind

00:01:05.638 --> 00:01:07.792
un ikh helf zi zeyer a sakh

00:01:08.254 --> 00:01:09.018
un

00:01:09.018 --> 00:01:10.259
in eyn tog

00:01:10.259 --> 00:01:11.640
kumt arayn

00:01:11.798 --> 00:01:13.693
a yid mit a froy

00:01:13.693 --> 00:01:15.169
in der shtub

00:01:15.169 --> 00:01:17.969
vos ikh hob gelebt mit der goye, dos iz geven zayn hoyz.

00:01:17.969 --> 00:01:20.049
s'iz nisht geven a vikhtik hoyz

00:01:20.049 --> 00:01:21.429
nor s'iz geven a WOHNUNG.

00:01:21.805 --> 00:01:23.039
un

00:01:23.039 --> 00:01:25.299
far dem hot di goye dertseylt

00:01:25.299 --> 00:01:26.928
az zi hot a yidish kind

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:30.171
hot er zeyer gevolt kenen dos yidishe

00:01:30.171 --> 00:01:30.860
kind.

00:01:31.609 --> 00:01:34.905
un eyn tsayt zi s- shmuest zikh op

00:01:34.905 --> 00:01:38.032
der dokter, er iz geven a dokter. er kumt tsu geyn

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:42.389
un er treft zikh mit mir, un er heybt on tsu mir redn yidish

00:01:42.389 --> 00:01:44.479
un ikh ken nisht keyn eyn vort yidish.

00:01:44.772 --> 00:01:48.124
se geyt nisht aroys keyn eyn vort yidish fun mayn mol.

00:01:48.366 --> 00:01:51.212
az er hot dos gezen, hot er ongehoybn mit mir poylish redn.

00:01:51.572 --> 00:01:54.353
er hot ongehoybn poylish redn, un me redt zikh op

00:01:54.353 --> 00:01:55.953
zogt er "veyst vos?

00:01:56.095 --> 00:01:57.760
ikh ken dir yetst helfn."

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:01.840
helfn, z- iz er aleyn orem geven, nor er hot gevust az ikh ken nokh gikher im helfn.

00:02:02.659 --> 00:02:06.855
ikh hob nokh gehat produktn demolst, UNK vosere produktn dos hob ikh nisht dertseylt.

00:02:07.182 --> 00:02:11.513
eyder der rus iz arayn, iz keyner nisht gevezn. UNK hot men geefnt di fabrikn

00:02:11.653 --> 00:02:14.080
un azoy, hot men geefnt fleysh

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:16.880
hobn mir undz mir getrogn dos fleysh mit der khaverte.

00:02:16.880 --> 00:02:21.490
m'hot geefnt laylekher, hobn mir getrogn laylekher. m'hot geefnt boyml, hobn mir getrogn boyml

00:02:21.490 --> 00:02:25.120
un m'hot a sakh zakhn ongetrogn, me zol hobn fun vanet zikh tsu shpayzn.

00:02:25.305 --> 00:02:27.796
hob ikh gehat a bisele tsu helfn

00:02:27.837 --> 00:02:29.870
take dem dokter, un

00:02:29.870 --> 00:02:32.850
take der froy vos zi hot gehat a kind hob ikh geholfn a sakh.

00:02:32.983 --> 00:02:37.027
un der dokter hot gezogt azoy. er hot mikh gehaltn azoy vi a eygn kind.

00:02:37.303 --> 00:02:40.672
nor vos iz? ikh zol im yetst a bisl helfn. dernokh dem vet er mir helfn.

00:02:40.965 --> 00:02:44.851
nor er hot ongehoybn tsu arbetn in a POLIKLINIKA.

00:02:44.851 --> 00:02:49.582
hot er gezogt, er vet mir gebn a spravke az ikh arbet, di rusn zoln mir nisht makhn gornisht.

00:02:49.875 --> 00:02:53.736
vet er mir aroysgebn a spravke az ikh arbet. vos vet zayn mayn arbet?

00:02:53.736 --> 00:02:56.602
ikh ken zitsn fir un tsvontsik sho bay dem telefon

00:02:56.693 --> 00:02:58.765
un er vet mir gebn az ikh arbet di gantse tsayt.

00:02:58.765 --> 00:03:02.576
vel ikh shoyn kenen zayn fray vos di rusn veln mir nisht tshepen az fun dem leb ikh.

00:03:02.582 --> 00:03:04.297
es iz azoy geven.

00:03:04.658 --> 00:03:06.997
er hot mir gegebn aza spravke

00:03:07.408 --> 00:03:10.659
un ikh hob shoyn ongehoybn forn demolst ⟨keyn⟩ Lutsk

00:03:10.969 --> 00:03:12.009
un Lemberik.

00:03:12.724 --> 00:03:15.722
ikh hob oyf yedn mark dortn gevezn

00:03:15.795 --> 00:03:18.269
un ikh hob gefirt a sakh skhoyre.

00:03:18.478 --> 00:03:20.412
un dos iz geven a groyse fardinst.

00:03:21.229 --> 00:03:23.993
demolst hob ikh gevorn a sakh shoyn

00:03:23.993 --> 00:03:26.184
shpa- mer gelt gehat

00:03:26.680 --> 00:03:29.931
un di polyakn zenen geforn keyn Poyln.

00:03:30.460 --> 00:03:34.014
hob ikh mit eyn polke geredt vos iz geven mayn khaverte oykhet

00:03:34.071 --> 00:03:37.232
az zi lozt mir di voynung iber mit di mebl

00:03:37.232 --> 00:03:38.942
un ikh vel ir batsoln

00:03:38.998 --> 00:03:41.422
un zi vet forn keyn Poyln. zi vet mir dos ales lozn.

00:03:41.547 --> 00:03:43.076
ikh hob ir batsolt

00:03:43.302 --> 00:03:46.749
un ikh hob disp- gegangen dortn vu me darf.

00:03:46.749 --> 00:03:48.539
ikh hob opgegebn a bite

00:03:48.539 --> 00:03:49.869
az dos iz mayn WOHNUNG.

00:03:49.869 --> 00:03:55.509
yo? dort iz geven ma- mayne zakhn UNK dernokh dem vel ikh tsunemen di goye tsu mir, un undz veln mir dortn voynen.

00:03:56.768 --> 00:03:58.494
un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu forn

00:03:58.494 --> 00:03:59.613
un tsu handlen.

00:03:59.991 --> 00:04:02.752
dervayle, di goyim dortn

00:04:02.927 --> 00:04:06.836
hobn gezogt "veystu vos? s'iz do do eyner a ZHYDOK."

00:04:07.213 --> 00:04:08.236
in Lutsk?

00:04:08.108 --> 00:04:09.182
in Lutsk.

00:04:09.441 --> 00:04:12.366
"er brengt undz a sakh biliker di trink sode"

00:04:12.366 --> 00:04:15.150
vayl trink sode iz geven a groyse opgang

00:04:15.150 --> 00:04:17.352
vayl di goyim hobn gehat a

00:04:17.352 --> 00:04:20.066
a brenung oyfn hartsn, zoln vern farbrent

00:04:20.663 --> 00:04:22.378
un s'hot zey shtark gebrent

00:04:22.772 --> 00:04:26.951
un di sode hobn zey getrunken, un dos hot zey geratevet. dos iz geven zeyer a groyse opgang.

00:04:27.261 --> 00:04:28.701
iz zey hobn mir gezogt

00:04:28.701 --> 00:04:31.848
az dort iz do a ZHYDOK. er brengt undz a sakh biliker.

00:04:31.848 --> 00:04:33.585
hob ikh gezogt "vos? a ZHYDOK?"

00:04:33.585 --> 00:04:36.485
zey hobn gevust az ikh bin a yidish kind, vayl dos iz shoyn geven farn rus

00:04:36.508 --> 00:04:38.780
zog ikh "ikh muz dem ZHYDOK kenen.

00:04:40.187 --> 00:04:41.261
in eyn

00:04:41.436 --> 00:04:45.463
tog, dos iz geven a mark tog, dakht zikh mir. ikh shtey mit skhoyre

00:04:45.756 --> 00:04:48.484
un di goye vayzt mir on, zogt zi "host a ZHYDOK.

00:04:48.490 --> 00:04:52.129
dos iz der ZHYDOK vos er m- vos er farkoyft ⟨undz⟩ biliker skhoyre."

00:04:52.472 --> 00:04:54.662
un ikh gey tsu, un ikh red im.

00:04:54.662 --> 00:04:56.562
yidish hob ikh nisht gekent redn.

00:04:56.562 --> 00:04:58.122
m'hot ongehoybn redn poylish.

00:04:58.122 --> 00:04:59.742
PANINA UNK

00:04:59.742 --> 00:05:00.704
m'hot ongehoybn redn.

00:05:00.704 --> 00:05:04.583
vos tustu du? vi azoy bistu ge-, m'hot ongehoybn azoy zikh oyfredn, yo?

00:05:04.875 --> 00:05:06.219
me redt zikh oyf

00:05:06.495 --> 00:05:11.568
un ikh gedenk nisht, dem tog dakht zikh gey ikh tsu im in shtub arayn. er hot gehat dort a voynung

00:05:12.250 --> 00:05:13.830
un me redt zikh oyf

00:05:13.853 --> 00:05:16.074
un ikh gey tsurik tsu der goye

00:05:16.131 --> 00:05:18.032
un ikh for keyn Lemberik tsurik

00:05:18.257 --> 00:05:24.528
un ikh breng ir a groysn kvantum mit skhoyre mit mayn khaverte tsuzamen. ikh hob zikh gehaltn alts mit mayn khaverte.

00:05:26.053 --> 00:05:29.821
un eyn mol bay nakht hot emetser vayzt oys tsugemoldn

00:05:29.821 --> 00:05:31.956
az s'iz do do a spekulantke

00:05:31.956 --> 00:05:34.147
vos zi firt skhoyre

00:05:34.609 --> 00:05:36.526
un me darf zi areshtirn.

00:05:37.630 --> 00:05:41.541
in ovnt bay nakht kumen tsu di N.K.V.D.

00:05:41.541 --> 00:05:42.655
di rusn

00:05:42.655 --> 00:05:45.960
un me areshtirt mir alts spekulantke.

00:05:46.759 --> 00:05:48.812
me nemt mir in der tfise

00:05:48.835 --> 00:05:51.244
un me git mir di STAT'YA

00:05:51.244 --> 00:05:53.353
hundert finef un tsvontsik.

00:05:53.353 --> 00:05:56.315
dos iz gevezn di STAT'YA spekulantke.

00:05:56.315 --> 00:05:57.520
ot dos gevezn.

00:05:58.015 --> 00:06:01.586
un ikh zits op in der tfise dray monat

00:06:02.031 --> 00:06:03.797
un mayn man

00:06:04.360 --> 00:06:06.340
vos er iz nokh demolts nisht geven mayn man

00:06:06.340 --> 00:06:08.691
az m'hot zikh geredt PAN PANI

00:06:08.899 --> 00:06:10.749
un er hot nisht gevust vi azoy ikh heys.

00:06:10.772 --> 00:06:15.122
er iz gegangen tsu di goyim. di goyim hobn gezogt az er zits- az ikh zits in Lemberik

00:06:15.122 --> 00:06:18.412
un ikh hob mikh lang nisht gezesn in Lemberik, ⟨nor⟩ ikh hob gezesn in Lutsk.

00:06:19.075 --> 00:06:22.413
ikh bin geven dort dray monatn, nor vos iz? mayne goyim

00:06:22.413 --> 00:06:23.965
hobn mir shuldik geven gelt.

00:06:23.965 --> 00:06:25.771
di skhoyre hot men mir ales tsugenumen.

00:06:25.771 --> 00:06:27.458
ales hot men konfeskirt

00:06:27.458 --> 00:06:29.868
nor di goyim hobn mir shuldik geven gelt

00:06:30.347 --> 00:06:33.547
iz dos gelt hobn zey gekoyft peklekh, un zey hobn mir geshikt.

00:06:33.672 --> 00:06:36.343
un di peklekh hob ikh in tfise a bisl geteylt.

00:06:36.343 --> 00:06:39.572
dort zenen gezesn shikses BANDEROVTSes

00:06:39.747 --> 00:06:41.817
yo? zey hobn gevust ikh bin a yidish kind.

00:06:41.817 --> 00:06:43.777
oder ikh hob azoy geredt gut

00:06:43.915 --> 00:06:46.794
azoy, zey hobn nisht geleygt azoy in akht shtark

00:06:46.986 --> 00:06:51.485
eyne iz dortn gezesn, un ikh hob ir gezogt az ikh ken epes a ZHYDOK eynem

00:06:51.677 --> 00:06:57.597
hot er, hot zi gezogt zi ken im. er iz a Ratner. er iz oyf kulyes gegangen. er iz ranirt, hot zi mir gezogt.

00:06:57.597 --> 00:06:59.537
ikh zog "ikh ken dokh nisht zayn nomen"

00:06:59.537 --> 00:07:02.640
un ikh gedenk nisht tsi zi hot mir oykhet nisht gezogt dem nomen.

00:07:03.034 --> 00:07:06.639
ikh hob opgezesn dray monatn. s'iz mir nisht geven gut in der tfise.

00:07:06.780 --> 00:07:10.908
kh'hob mir oysgegangen vashn di koridorn kedey ikh zol krign nokh a shtikl broyt

00:07:11.100 --> 00:07:14.193
un s'iz geven umedik, un m'hot geshlofn oyfn shteyn.

00:07:14.193 --> 00:07:16.814
s'iz nisht geven mit vos zikh tsudekn, dos zelbe.

00:07:16.838 --> 00:07:19.450
s'iz geven, s'hot geheysn PARASHA

00:07:19.450 --> 00:07:23.643
m'hot dortn, iz, m'iz, m'hot nisht gelozt in der klozet geyn. m'hot in shtub ge-

00:07:23.643 --> 00:07:25.550
s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer shver.

00:07:25.550 --> 00:07:28.813
ikh bin shoyn dort geven efsher akhtsn a halb yor.

00:07:29.157 --> 00:07:30.799
mayn khaverte iz geven a sakh elter

00:07:30.799 --> 00:07:33.066
un ikh hob zikh alts gehaltn mit der khaverte gut.

00:07:34.152 --> 00:07:35.563
dernokh dem

00:07:35.721 --> 00:07:38.291
hobn mir opgezesn d- efsher dray monat.

00:07:38.291 --> 00:07:40.139
es iz gekumen in eyn tog

00:07:40.139 --> 00:07:42.380
un m'hot gezogt "yetst hot ir di MISHPAT."

00:07:42.454 --> 00:07:44.135
s'iz gekumen tsu MISHPAT.

00:07:44.563 --> 00:07:47.004
hob ikh zikh shoyn zeyer gefreyt, di MISHPAT.

00:07:47.331 --> 00:07:49.063
m'iz gekumen in a tog.

00:07:49.103 --> 00:07:51.696
me geyt tsu dem MISHPAT, ikh mit mayn khaverte.

00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:57.500
kh'hob a MISHPAT az take a hundert finef un tsvontsik, dos iz spekulantke, dos iz dray yor tfise

00:07:57.507 --> 00:07:58.648
darf ikh krign.

00:08:00.510 --> 00:08:02.448
me heybt mir on mishpetn

00:08:02.448 --> 00:08:03.964
un der prekuror

00:08:04.138 --> 00:08:06.089
git mir dray yor tfise.

00:08:06.282 --> 00:08:11.467
tsvishn dem, a advokatke iz geven, a yidishe dakht zikh UNK ⟨iz zi⟩ geven a yidishe dakht zikh, di advokatke

00:08:11.467 --> 00:08:17.112
un zi shtelt zikh aroyf. zogt zi "vemen vilt ir gebn tfise dray yor? dos iz dokh a kind

00:08:17.112 --> 00:08:22.042
vos zi hot ibergelebt azoy fil" un ikh hob ir a bisele dertseylt mayn iberlebenish.

00:08:22.042 --> 00:08:23.972
"far vemen vilt ir gebn tfise?"

00:08:23.972 --> 00:08:25.715
un zi hot shtark sheyn geredt.

00:08:26.008 --> 00:08:29.038
hobn zey gegangen, zey hobn gelozt, zey hobn zikh gegangen rotn.

00:08:29.038 --> 00:08:30.418
zey hobn zikh barotn

00:08:30.418 --> 00:08:31.718
un zey kumen aroys

00:08:31.718 --> 00:08:35.028
un zogn "veyst vos? du krigst dray yor ⟨ZA VYSHCHENIYA⟩

00:08:35.087 --> 00:08:37.885
krigstu, nisht keyn tfise, nor ⟨ZA VYSHCHENIYA⟩ du vest mer

00:08:36.876 --> 00:08:37.983
AL TNAY

00:08:37.885 --> 00:08:40.340
az dos iz AL TNAY az du vest mer

00:08:40.340 --> 00:08:41.425
nisht handlen."

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:50.319
un ikh gey nokh in der tfise. me re- me nekhtikt nokh iber, un mayn khaverte lozt men oykhet nokh. a dank mir bafrayt men zi oykhet.

00:08:51.338 --> 00:08:53.646
mir bafrayt men in der fri

00:08:53.646 --> 00:08:58.009
un ikh gey, ikh tu, ⟨ikh hob nor⟩ gehat a, nisht keyn gutn mantl ongeton

00:08:58.009 --> 00:08:59.856
un ikh gey in gas

00:08:59.856 --> 00:09:03.549
un in dem gas tref ikh mayn ma- mayn yetstikn man.

00:09:02.906 --> 00:09:04.326
tsukunftikn man, yo.

00:09:04.146 --> 00:09:05.079
tref ikh im.

00:09:05.079 --> 00:09:10.521
er kukt mir on, zogt er "fun vanet kumstu? du host dokh badorfn zitsn in Lemberik. fun vanet kumstu yetst?"

00:09:10.521 --> 00:09:12.824
zog ikh "ikh hob gezesn in Lutsk, nisht in Lemberik."

00:09:12.824 --> 00:09:15.750
zogt er "dikh hob ikh nisht gevust dayn nomen, vi azoy du heyst" zogt er.

00:09:15.908 --> 00:09:22.534
"ikh hob gevust" zogt er "m'hot aykh gerufn OLESHKA, HALA hot men dikh gerufn, oder ikh hob nisht gevust vu du zitst. ven ikh veys vu du zitst helf ikh dikh dokh."

00:09:23.063 --> 00:09:27.624
ot dos iz geven a terets, vayl mayn man iz nisht geven a, er iz geven a guter zhulik, mayn man, demolst.

00:09:27.624 --> 00:09:30.701
efsher ⟨dos fardrist zikh⟩ vos ikh zog dos, oder azoy iz gevezn.

00:09:30.808 --> 00:09:32.540
yo

00:09:33.711 --> 00:09:35.986
zogt er "kum tsu mir in shtub arayn"

00:09:35.986 --> 00:09:38.070
un ikh gey tsu im in shtub arayn

00:09:38.070 --> 00:09:39.712
un er zogt "veyst vos?

00:09:39.718 --> 00:09:41.366
ikh vel dir shoyn yetst a sakh helfn"

00:09:41.878 --> 00:09:42.702
zogt er.

00:09:42.702 --> 00:09:44.525
"vi du vest shoyn brengen skhoyre

00:09:44.525 --> 00:09:47.345
vel ikh shoyn dikh ophitn di skhoyre, zol nisht onkumen

00:09:47.345 --> 00:09:50.655
az du vest UNK" vayl ikh hob keyn ander veg nisht gehat. ikh hob nisht gekent andersh lebn

00:09:50.695 --> 00:09:52.235
vayl s'iz geven zeyer shlekht.

00:09:52.611 --> 00:09:55.035
un tsvishn dem, zogt er "veystu vos?"

00:09:55.328 --> 00:09:56.618
neyn, ikh hob im gezogt

00:09:56.618 --> 00:09:59.198
"veystu vos? ikh volt khasene gehat mit dir trots dem.

00:09:59.198 --> 00:10:02.248
far vos? ikh darf hobn a spravke az ikh for Lemberik Lutsk.

00:10:02.248 --> 00:10:05.670
dos vet mir rateven az di N.K.V.D. vet mikh mer nisht areshtirn."

00:10:07.191 --> 00:10:08.552
zog ikh azoy.

00:10:09.368 --> 00:10:11.499
keyn khasene hobn mir nisht gemakht, nor m'hot zikh

00:10:11.499 --> 00:10:13.305
gegangen ⟨un zikh z- dershribn⟩.

00:10:13.305 --> 00:10:14.554
m'hot zikh dershribn.

00:10:14.554 --> 00:10:15.701
m'hot ongehoybn

00:10:15.701 --> 00:10:16.516
lebn.

