m'hot gemakht dort a bronfn getrunken, un m'hot ongehoybn lebn.

00:10:20.337 --> 00:10:22.029
m'hot ongehoybn lebn

00:10:22.029 --> 00:10:24.380
un demolst, ven ikh bin geforn keyn Lemberik

00:10:24.488 --> 00:10:29.698
hot mayn man shoyn oyf der statsye, tsurik vegs, hot mayn man opgehit oyf der statsye

00:10:29.698 --> 00:10:31.798
un er fleg mir di skhoyre nemen

00:10:31.798 --> 00:10:32.432
un ikh

00:10:32.432 --> 00:10:33.729
fleg geyn, yo?

00:10:33.870 --> 00:10:35.180
eyn mol

00:10:35.338 --> 00:10:37.391
koyf ikh on a valizke mit heyvn

00:10:37.515 --> 00:10:40.158
un ikh for mit der valizke mit heyvn dortn.

00:10:40.992 --> 00:10:43.213
un ikh hob epes nisht bamerkt mayn man

00:10:43.759 --> 00:10:45.747
un se kumt on a N.K.D.V. s-

00:10:45.747 --> 00:10:51.299
se kumt on a N.K.V.D., un er git mir di heyvn a konfeskir, un er git mir a khap.

00:10:51.299 --> 00:10:53.439
un er firt mir tsu di politsey.

00:10:53.496 --> 00:10:55.633
un mayn man git a shprung aroys

00:10:56.010 --> 00:10:59.598
un er nemt di heyvn. zogt er "du gey mit di heyvn. ikh vel mit im erleydikn.

00:11:00.060 --> 00:11:01.677
ikh vel shoyn mit im erleydikn."

00:11:01.677 --> 00:11:04.189
un ikh kum in shtub arayn shoyn mit di heyvn

00:11:04.785 --> 00:11:06.517
un er hot shoyn mit im erleydikt.

00:11:06.557 --> 00:11:09.453
kh'veys nisht vi azoy, ⟨oder⟩ UNK mikh ho- mikh hot men gelozt.

00:11:09.831 --> 00:11:16.187
azoy m'hot shoyn gezen az ikh hob di dray yor ⟨ZA VYSHCHENIYA⟩, un ikh hob shoyn geshvangert mit mayn zun dray monatn.

00:11:16.227 --> 00:11:20.001
az s'iz shoyn shver, hot men ongehoybn redn, undz darfn mir forn keyn

00:11:20.023 --> 00:11:20.880
Poyln.

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:23.274
un fun Poyln, un m'vet shoyn forn keyn Daytshland.

00:11:23.871 --> 00:11:25.299
un m'hot opgeredt

00:11:25.407 --> 00:11:28.269
un m'hot gegangen. m'hot erleydikt papirn

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.951
un m'hot aroysgeforn

00:11:29.951 --> 00:11:31.082
keyn Poyln.

00:11:31.082 --> 00:11:33.754
in Poyln zenen mir geven in WALBRZYCH

00:11:33.827 --> 00:11:37.443
zeks mo- zeks vokhn zenen mir geven in a KIBUTS.

00:11:37.443 --> 00:11:40.183
dos iz geven Ge- nokh ⟨Geltser⟩ pogrom.

00:11:40.223 --> 00:11:42.186
un undz ho'mir zeyer moyre gehat

00:11:42.186 --> 00:11:48.755
nor vos iz, ze'mir, m'iz geven mit gever dortn, un m'hot opgehit, nor zeyer mit shrek gema- geva- geven demolst.

00:11:48.947 --> 00:11:51.000
m'iz geven dortn zeks vokhn.

00:11:51.208 --> 00:11:54.175
dernokh dem hot men gezogt "ir greyt zikh tsu in veg arayn."

00:11:54.175 --> 00:11:57.109
ikh hob shoyn demolts zeks monat geshvangert mit mayn zun.

00:11:57.402 --> 00:11:59.845
hot men gezogt azoy. "me tor gornisht mitnemen

00:11:59.845 --> 00:12:01.524
nor me darf geyn tsu fus

00:12:01.524 --> 00:12:03.791
zeks kilometer darf men geyn tsu fus.

00:12:03.949 --> 00:12:05.596
greyt zikh tsu tsu dem veg."

00:12:05.434 --> 00:12:07.807
dos iz shoyn geven nayntsn hundert zeks un fertsik.

00:12:07.307 --> 00:12:12.633
dos iz geven shoyn anfang zeks un fertsik, vayl zeks un fertsik iz dokh mayn zun in Daytshland geboyrn, yo?

00:12:09.298 --> 00:12:10.186
yo.

00:12:11.087 --> 00:12:12.060
yo.

00:12:13.450 --> 00:12:14.670
un eyn nakht

00:12:14.670 --> 00:12:18.320
hot men undz gezogt vos me darf redn, on a dokumentn un on

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:22.460
gornisht, me zol zogn vos zey zogn. m'iz ⟨grishishe⟩ grikhishe l- yidn

00:12:22.900 --> 00:12:30.673
un m'hot geshvartst di grenets, ikh mitn boykh, un ⟨ikh hob mit mir⟩ gornisht gekent nemen. m'iz zeyer geven hungerik. m'iz ongekumen keyn Tshekhay.

00:12:30.932 --> 00:12:34.149
m'iz ongekumen keyn Tshekhay. dos iz gevezn

00:12:34.594 --> 00:12:37.223
B- ikh gedenk nisht di shtot in Tshekhay.

00:12:37.223 --> 00:12:39.211
m'iz geven dort a dray tog

00:12:39.505 --> 00:12:44.933
un m'iz alts geven hungerik. m'hot epes gehat a por dolar demolst. m'hot gekoyft frukhtn. m'hot gegesn.

00:12:45.090 --> 00:12:49.100
un demolst eyn nakht iz geven fun mayn shtetl a ZEMLYAK

00:12:49.225 --> 00:12:52.841
hot epes a shtikl broyt gegebn. ikh hob geshvangert. ikh bin geven mitn

00:12:52.841 --> 00:12:54.883
boykh, un ikh bin geven zeyer hungerik

00:12:54.883 --> 00:12:55.800
oykhet.

00:12:56.262 --> 00:12:58.747
me kumt on dernokh dem keyn ⟨Estraykh⟩.

00:12:58.747 --> 00:13:00.187
in ⟨Estraykh⟩

00:13:00.261 --> 00:13:03.211
hot undzer, di khevre

00:13:03.211 --> 00:13:05.691
ibergenumen dem lager, zenen gevorn di

00:13:05.691 --> 00:13:07.151
politsey fun dem lager.

00:13:07.602 --> 00:13:11.190
iz undz gevorn beser a bisl. m'hot shoyn gehat mer tsu esn

00:13:11.770 --> 00:13:14.379
nor vos iz? mir iz nokhgegangen

00:13:14.807 --> 00:13:21.331
vos ikh bin geven zeyer fun a frumer heym, un ikh hob nisht genumen keyn khupe kidushn, dos kind keile, s'vet geboyrn vern a mazer.

00:13:21.928 --> 00:13:24.228
iz mir dos di gantse tsayt nokhgegangen.

00:13:24.228 --> 00:13:27.018
hob ikh gezogt tsu mayn man, "veyst vos?

00:13:27.396 --> 00:13:29.666
undz darfn mir nemen khupe kidushn yetst.

00:13:29.666 --> 00:13:31.636
s'iz do ver, m'vet gebn khupe kidushn."

00:13:31.783 --> 00:13:35.216
s'iz nokh geven tsvey porfelker vos zey hobn zikh nor dray tog gekent

00:13:35.216 --> 00:13:37.346
zogt zi "m'vet makhn dray khasenes bazamen."

00:13:38.044 --> 00:13:39.846
m'iz gekumen in eyn ovnt.

00:13:39.846 --> 00:13:40.673
me makht

00:13:40.673 --> 00:13:44.276
dray khasenes. me greyt tsu, me nemt a orkester, keyn

00:13:44.276 --> 00:13:48.213
velon hobn mir nisht gehat gornisht, nor m'hot undz bashit mit papir.

00:13:48.945 --> 00:13:50.781
me makht di khasene.

00:13:50.781 --> 00:13:54.409
s'iz geven sheyn un gut. ikh zitst mit di tsvey kales.

00:13:54.409 --> 00:13:58.692
un ikh zog epes "mayn man," hobn zey ongehoybn tsu lakhn. "vos heyst, mit dayn man?"

00:13:59.712 --> 00:14:05.880
"dayn man UNK dray tog nokh di kha- n- nor vos khasene gehat, ober ikh bin shoyn a halb yor mit mayn man. ikh shvanger shoyn mit mayn zun."

00:14:05.880 --> 00:14:08.170
hob ikh zey gezogt, er iz shoyn mayn man a halb yor.

00:14:08.170 --> 00:14:09.561
⟨nu⟩, dos gedenk ikh.

00:14:10.765 --> 00:14:13.476
m'iz geven nokh in dem lager, ikh gedenk nisht vifl

00:14:13.701 --> 00:14:15.259
un m'iz aroysgeforn keyn Daytshland.

00:14:15.259 --> 00:14:16.937
m'iz geforn keyn Daytshland.

00:14:16.937 --> 00:14:19.719
in Daytshland hot men undz gegebn shoyn tsimern

00:14:20.637 --> 00:14:22.588
vu zent ir geven in Daytshland?

00:14:21.227 --> 00:14:24.360
akhtsn man bazamen. in Daytshland, in Bamberg zenen mir gevezn.

00:14:24.417 --> 00:14:27.932
m'hot undz gegebn mit akhtsn tsuz- mentshn tsuzamen

00:14:27.932 --> 00:14:30.553
un yeder eyner hot zikh gemakht a shtibl

00:14:30.964 --> 00:14:32.409
bazunder, yo?

00:14:32.466 --> 00:14:35.615
un ikh hob shoyn demolst geshvangert in nayntn monat.

00:14:35.993 --> 00:14:38.360
ikh eyne bin geven azoy mit a

00:14:37.731 --> 00:14:38.568
yo

00:14:38.360 --> 00:14:40.430
mit a, vos ikh hob badorfn geboyrn a kind.

00:14:40.482 --> 00:14:44.500
iz mayn man gegangen in vald arbetn nokh mit khevre, me zol hobn

00:14:44.500 --> 00:14:46.930
tsu heytsn holts, un me zol zayn far dem kind

00:14:46.930 --> 00:14:49.487
varem in dem shtibl. s'iz geven a ⟨kasarne⟩ azane groyse

00:14:50.995 --> 00:14:52.305
un eyn tog

00:14:52.328 --> 00:14:54.746
hob ikh shoyn gegangen geboyrn mayn zun.

00:14:54.746 --> 00:14:57.420
iz mayn man mit di khevre, m'hot mitgeforn

00:14:57.420 --> 00:14:59.480
in daytshishn shpitol in BAMBERG

00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:00.830
ikh zol geyn geboyrn.

00:15:00.934 --> 00:15:02.598
ikh bin gekumen ahin

00:15:02.841 --> 00:15:08.828
iz der, un me lozt mir iber aleyn dortn, un ikh hob shtark moyre gehat. ikh hob nokh gehat dem pakhed far di daytshn

00:15:08.828 --> 00:15:11.643
vi zey lozn mir iber dortn aleyn.

00:15:12.662 --> 00:15:14.377
zey hobn mir gelozt aleyn

00:15:14.805 --> 00:15:16.908
⟨iz⟩ dos iz geven a zeyger tsvelef

00:15:16.932 --> 00:15:20.149
ikh hob gehert shtark geveyn. mayn zun iz geboyrn dray a zeyger.

00:15:20.931 --> 00:15:25.872
nokh dray a zeyger hot men mir opgereynikt ales, un ikh hob alts mit dem pakhed gegangen.

00:15:25.872 --> 00:15:27.340
un m'hot mir genumen

00:15:27.340 --> 00:15:31.618
oyf a tsimer vu s'iz shoyn gelign yidishe froyen fun lager fun maynem

00:15:31.618 --> 00:15:33.727
un s'iz mir shoyn geven a sakh laykhter

00:15:33.727 --> 00:15:37.547
hobn zey gezogt "veyst vos? m'vet im makhn dem bris in shpitol

00:15:37.907 --> 00:15:42.437
un m'hot shoyn di shvesters a bisele untergekoyft, undz zenen shoyn geven zeyer gut

00:15:42.437 --> 00:15:48.680
hobn zey gezogt "m'vet makhn dem bris, un nokhn bris vet men dir brengen dayn zun glaykh zolstu im zeygn," un s'iz geven ales gut.

00:15:49.635 --> 00:15:52.599
in Daytshland zenen mir gevezn nokh

00:15:52.723 --> 00:15:54.551
efsher tsen monat

00:15:54.551 --> 00:15:56.784
tsi mer zenen mir nokh geven in Daytshland

00:15:57.043 --> 00:16:01.060
oder s'iz geven shver. zey hobn gehat epes a shtikl gesheft un m'hot

00:16:01.060 --> 00:16:03.410
fardint a bisl. es iz nokh geven shver tsu lebn.

00:16:03.642 --> 00:16:07.030
nor vos iz? tsvishn dem hobn mir undz mir gefunen di kroyvim fun Amerike

00:16:07.030 --> 00:16:10.891
hobn zey undz ongehoybn zeyer a sakh peklekh shikn un tsu helfn, iz shoyn geven a bisele beser.

00:16:11.218 --> 00:16:13.476
un der mame's a shvester

00:16:13.476 --> 00:16:19.408
az m'hot zi shoyn gefunen, hot zi ⟨nor⟩ geshribn ikh zol kumen keyn Amerike, vayl in PALESTINE iz a milkhome, me zol nisht forn

00:16:19.408 --> 00:16:20.645
keyn PALESTINE.

00:16:20.938 --> 00:16:27.243
oder mikh hot alts getsu- getsoygn, un mayn man oykhet, keyn PALESTINE. mayn man hot in a tog gezogt

00:16:27.385 --> 00:16:32.596
"ven ikh hob mayn froy vu tsu lozn mitn kind, for ikh kemfn tsu Erets Yisroel.

00:16:32.596 --> 00:16:35.259
oder er hot nisht gehat vemen tsu lozn mir mitn kind.

00:16:35.974 --> 00:16:37.790
s'hot nisht gedoyert lang.

00:16:37.999 --> 00:16:40.018
mayn zun iz shoyn geven

00:16:40.497 --> 00:16:43.258
a yor, onderhalbn yor iz er ⟨hot⟩ shoyn geven demolst.

00:16:43.585 --> 00:16:45.328
er hot zikh geshpilt in zamd

00:16:45.328 --> 00:16:47.898
un m'hot reklamirt di yidishe medine.

00:16:48.057 --> 00:16:51.139
demolst gedenk ikh. er hot zikh geshpilt kleyn kind in zamd

00:16:51.178 --> 00:16:53.804
un ikh her az s'iz do di yidishe medine.

00:16:52.984 --> 00:16:55.509
dos iz shoyn may akht un fertsik.

00:16:55.313 --> 00:16:58.547
dos iz may akht un fertsik. azoy darf, azoy darf es zayn.

00:16:59.464 --> 00:17:01.938
un me darf ale aroysforn keyn Daytshland

00:17:02.620 --> 00:17:05.380
heyst es fun Daytshland aroysforn keyn

00:17:04.324 --> 00:17:05.718
keyn Erets Yisroel

00:17:05.438 --> 00:17:09.594
keyn, nisht keyn Erets Yisroel. ⟨m'vet⟩ fo- durkhforn farshidene pletser nor.

00:17:09.099 --> 00:17:09.970
yo.

00:17:09.594 --> 00:17:15.000
un m'hot nor durkhgeforn Tshekhay un dernokh dem ⟨Estraykh⟩ un dernokh dem

00:17:15.006 --> 00:17:17.424
zenen mir gekumen keyn Daytshland

00:17:17.424 --> 00:17:18.749
un in Daytshland

00:17:18.749 --> 00:17:20.770
hobn mir shoyn ongehoybn lebn dortn

00:17:21.199 --> 00:17:22.661
dos hot ir shoyn gezogt

00:17:21.520 --> 00:17:23.301
dortn shoyn, yo

00:17:22.836 --> 00:17:25.479
Daytshland.. fun Daytshland vu zent ir geforn?

00:17:23.358 --> 00:17:24.347
yo, yo.

00:17:24.355 --> 00:17:28.711
fun Daytshland hobn mir geforn, un me hot zikh oyfgeze- keyn F-

00:17:28.711 --> 00:17:31.361
Frankraykh. zenen mir geven in Frankraykh zeks vokhn

00:17:29.215 --> 00:17:30.019
Frank-

00:17:30.818 --> 00:17:32.044
keyn MARSEILLE.

00:17:31.645 --> 00:17:32.941
in MARSEILLE

00:17:32.941 --> 00:17:34.521
un der zun iz shoyn geven

00:17:34.521 --> 00:17:36.531
a yor mit zibn monat

00:17:36.531 --> 00:17:39.321
iz er shoyn a, mit akht monat iz er geven demolst der zun.

00:17:39.321 --> 00:17:41.460
s'iz geven oykhet ⟨zeyere⟩ shvere tsaytn

00:17:41.652 --> 00:17:45.302
oder m'hot shoyn alts gevart, me zol undz nemen keyn Erets Yisroel.

00:17:45.302 --> 00:17:51.783
un ikh hob nokh gehat demolts zeyer a sakh, vos ikh hob gevolt zeyer Erets Yisroel shtark. dos hot mir shtark getsoygn tsu dem.

00:17:52.452 --> 00:17:54.893
un eyn tog hot men undz genumen

00:17:55.168 --> 00:17:57.300
keyn, keyn, oyf der shif.

00:17:55.303 --> 00:17:56.225
oyf a shif

00:17:57.300 --> 00:18:01.544
m'hot undz oyfgezetst oyf der shif, CASERTA hot zi geheysn

00:18:01.544 --> 00:18:04.106
a shif fun ki vos m'hot gefirt.

00:18:04.956 --> 00:18:11.396
m'hot undz oyfgezetst dort, un ikh hob zikh shtark shlekht gefilt oyf der shif. ikh hob zeyer gebrokhn. mayn zun hot shtark gebrokhn

00:18:11.416 --> 00:18:15.430
un s'iz geven a dokter vos hot mir gegebn ZRIKOT. ikh hob zikh beser gefilt

00:18:16.313 --> 00:18:19.560
un dos iz zeyer nisht geven legal. m'hot nisht getort

00:18:19.560 --> 00:18:23.800
forn, un m'iz ongekumen di vasern tsu Erets Yisroel, hot men gezogt vos mir ⟨zoln⟩ redn

00:18:23.800 --> 00:18:27.020
az se kumen grikhishe yidn, me zol undz nisht khapn

00:18:27.020 --> 00:18:29.691
di f- di englender hobn badorfn khapn

00:18:29.691 --> 00:18:32.910
me zol zeyer ⟨opakht⟩ gebn, me ken bombardirn. m'iz geven in a groysn

00:18:32.910 --> 00:18:34.740
pakhed. ikh bin geven mit a kind

00:18:35.027 --> 00:18:37.333
oder m'iz ongekumen keyn HAIFA.

00:18:37.390 --> 00:18:40.686
m'iz aropgegangen in HAIFA. m'iz shoyn geven zeyer gliklekh.

00:18:40.686 --> 00:18:41.930
m'hot undz gegebn

00:18:41.930 --> 00:18:44.900
tsu esn demolst, un m'hot undz gefirt keyn PARDES

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:46.860
CHANA in a lager.

00:18:46.860 --> 00:18:49.331
zenen mir dortn geven zeks vokhn in dem lager

00:18:49.675 --> 00:18:51.289
un nokh dem lager

00:18:51.362 --> 00:18:52.486
zenen mir

00:18:52.628 --> 00:18:54.388
geve- ongekumen

00:18:54.388 --> 00:18:58.252
d- m'hot undz gezogt, tomer du vilst forn in RAMLE, ⟨ir zolt⟩ krign a WOHNUNG

00:18:58.252 --> 00:18:59.928
un d'vest blaybn dort in RAMLE.

00:19:00.255 --> 00:19:03.922
mayn zun iz shoyn geven demolst a yor mit tsen monat

00:19:03.922 --> 00:19:08.782
un vi azoy ikh hob im gebodn, iz oykhet geven CASERTAS ve- ka- di lagern farshidene

00:19:08.782 --> 00:19:10.682
fleg ikh nemen a vane vaser

00:19:10.682 --> 00:19:12.252
un onvaremen oyf der zun

00:19:12.252 --> 00:19:13.902
un ikh fleg im azoy oysbodn.

00:19:14.042 --> 00:19:19.335
un me fleg geyn in kikh, un me fleg krign esn. s'iz undz geven a bisele beser, vayl esn hot men beser gegebn

00:19:20.067 --> 00:19:22.811
un dernokh dem ikh bin avekgeforn tsu BAMBERG

00:19:22.969 --> 00:19:25.224
⟨⟩ ir redt dokh shoyn vegn RAMLE

00:19:25.028 --> 00:19:27.486
v- heyst es fun, b- avade

00:19:27.559 --> 00:19:29.446
ikh hob ge- SLICHA, kh'hob gehat a toes

00:19:28.403 --> 00:19:29.224
KEN

00:19:29.446 --> 00:19:31.521
yo, undz ze'mir gekumen keyn RAMLE.

00:19:31.521 --> 00:19:34.471
in RAMLE hot men gekrign a arabishe voynung.

00:19:35.203 --> 00:19:40.580
undz ho'mir, ikh hob shoyn gehat adresn fun Amerike, vayl m'hot undz shoyn, shoyn in Daytshland geholfn.

00:19:40.580 --> 00:19:43.148
ikh hob ongehoybn shraybn briv keyn Amerike.

00:19:43.148 --> 00:19:45.941
ikh hob ongehoybn tsu krign gelt fun Amerike.

00:19:45.941 --> 00:19:47.798
a groyse hilf hot men gehat, vayl me

00:19:47.798 --> 00:19:50.388
m'hot gekrign a arabishe voynung, oder m'hot gornisht gehat.

00:19:50.388 --> 00:19:52.778
m'hot nisht gehat keyn frizhider. m'hot nisht gehat

00:19:52.778 --> 00:19:54.285
keyn mebl. s'iz gornisht

00:19:54.285 --> 00:19:57.033
hot men nisht gehat. az zey hobn undz ongehoybn helfn

00:19:57.782 --> 00:20:05.680
dernokh dem hobn mir oykhet gearbet. ikh hob gearbet farshidene arbetn. mayn man hot gearbet oykhet in a plats vos er hot oykhet gut fardint.

00:20:05.123 --> 00:20:06.990
bay vos hot gearbet ayer man?

00:20:05.983 --> 00:20:08.137
er hot gearbet mayn man in a

00:20:08.228 --> 00:20:11.259
epes in a UNK gearbet, az er hot oykhet fardint

00:20:11.957 --> 00:20:16.456
un dernokh dem hot men fardint a bisl gelt, hot men gekoyft a besere voynung

00:20:16.665 --> 00:20:20.655
un m'hot dortn nokh gearbet a bisl. undz hobn mir zikh farnumen mit gendz shtopn.

00:20:20.655 --> 00:20:22.955
m'hot geshtopt di gendz, un m'hot farkoyft.

00:20:22.955 --> 00:20:25.045
m'hot gemakht a bisl gelt fun dem.

00:20:25.045 --> 00:20:27.900
m'hot gekoyft a besere voynung, aleyn a WOHNUNG

00:20:27.900 --> 00:20:29.635
s'iz geven azoy vi a vile

00:20:30.030 --> 00:20:32.774
un mayn man hot dernokh dem gekoyft a mashin

00:20:33.270 --> 00:20:37.887
a last oyto, un er hot ongehoybn tsu arbetn oyf dem last oyto.

00:20:38.350 --> 00:20:40.605
er hot shoyn a bisl beser fardint

00:20:40.662 --> 00:20:44.303
un dernokh dem, far dem iz nokh geboyrn gevorn di tokhter

00:20:44.303 --> 00:20:48.232
heyst es nokh, vifl nokh fir yor iz geboyrn gevorn di tokhter

00:20:48.492 --> 00:20:49.923
do in RAMLE.

00:20:49.923 --> 00:20:53.430
in UNK in shpitol iz geboyrn gevorn di tokhter tsvishn dem.

00:20:53.520 --> 00:20:57.769
s'iz geven zeyer shver mit tsvey kinder, vayl undz ho'mir in anfang nor in eyn shtub gevoynt

00:20:57.769 --> 00:21:02.189
mit tsvey kinder. m'hot nisht gehat keyn gaz. m'hot nisht gehat gornisht. m'hot UNK oyf a PRIMUS

00:21:02.189 --> 00:21:03.579
gevaremt di vaser.

00:21:03.932 --> 00:21:05.570
es iz nisht geven keyn vindlen

00:21:05.570 --> 00:21:10.450
hob ikh a vindl afile ⟨vos s'iz⟩ geven nas, fleg ikh oystrikenen bay dem lomp, un nokh a mol viklen di

00:21:10.450 --> 00:21:12.499
di tokhter, vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn vindlen.

00:21:13.568 --> 00:21:18.540
un dernokh dem ven me hot shoyn getoysht di voynung iz geven vos a mol beser. mayn man hot shoyn mer fardint

00:21:18.732 --> 00:21:22.961
un m'hot azoy gevoynt nokh dortn tsvey un draysik yor.

00:21:23.153 --> 00:21:25.695
nor tsvishn dem hobn mayne kinder gelernt.

00:21:25.870 --> 00:21:27.750
di tokhter iz gegangen, zi hot geendikt

00:21:27.750 --> 00:21:30.150
TICHO- de- koydem hot der zun geendikt TICHON

00:21:30.150 --> 00:21:32.180
un er iz gegangen lernen in universitet

00:21:32.282 --> 00:21:34.267
hot geendikt dem ershtn TOR

00:21:34.476 --> 00:21:38.857
M.A. dernokh dem hot er geen- B.A., dernokh dem hot er geendikt M.A. der zun.

00:21:39.117 --> 00:21:43.400
hot oykhet a bisl tsugearbet un gelernt. di tokhter hot avade geendikt TICHON

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:45.441
un s'iz gegangen in a PNIMIYA

00:21:45.441 --> 00:21:47.616
un ⟨geven gut⟩ lernen dray yor.

00:21:48.128 --> 00:21:52.695
dray yor hot zi geendikt dortn, un s'hot undz gekost zeyer a sakh gelt, vayl dos iz geven a PNIMIYA.

00:21:52.701 --> 00:21:57.060
mayn man hot gearbet zeyer shver kedey di kinder ⟨tsu lernen⟩. er hot gezogt azoy.

00:21:57.060 --> 00:22:00.390
"undz ho'mir nisht gelernt, viln mir di kinder zol zayn gelernt

00:22:00.565 --> 00:22:02.128
un s'zol zayn zey gut."

00:22:02.286 --> 00:22:05.177
un dos iz yetst gevorn azoy vos di kinder

00:22:05.177 --> 00:22:06.448
zenen gelernt

00:22:06.471 --> 00:22:11.224
un zey hobn zeyer sheyn parnose, un zey helfn yetst vifl zey kenen oykhet undz

00:22:11.618 --> 00:22:13.063
vayl se geyt zey gut.

00:22:13.086 --> 00:22:13.957
zeyer sheyn.

00:22:13.812 --> 00:22:15.122
yetst iz azoy.

00:22:15.297 --> 00:22:16.742
kh'hob a gutn man

00:22:17.035 --> 00:22:19.276
dos iz oykhet d- hinter der mame's

00:22:19.276 --> 00:22:20.825
pleytse vos zi shteyt.

00:22:22.419 --> 00:22:23.869
mayn man hert ⟨nisht ⟩ UNK

00:22:22.519 --> 00:22:25.490
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt betn nor, di kin- ir hot

00:22:25.490 --> 00:22:26.460
a zun

00:22:26.417 --> 00:22:27.917
yo, yo.

00:22:26.460 --> 00:22:27.850
un a tokhter

00:22:27.850 --> 00:22:29.810
un vifl eyniklekh, got tsu danken?

00:22:28.727 --> 00:22:30.317
finef eyniklekh hob ikh.

00:22:30.349 --> 00:22:31.794
finef eyniklekh

00:22:31.017 --> 00:22:31.967
yo.

00:22:32.290 --> 00:22:33.448
farshtey ikh.

00:22:42.162 --> 00:22:45.306
yetst vil ikh aykh zogn eyn zakh az ikh hob a gutn man.

00:22:45.306 --> 00:22:46.774
ikh hob gute kinder

00:22:46.774 --> 00:22:50.351
un a dank zey bin ikh gevorn a bisele tsu zikh gekumen.

00:22:50.351 --> 00:22:51.802
dos vos ikh ken aykh zogn.

00:22:51.802 --> 00:22:53.597
do shtel ikh aykh for mayn man

00:22:54.210 --> 00:22:57.599
er heyst YECHEZKEL KOTLER, un ikh gey nokh zayn nomen

00:22:57.599 --> 00:22:58.609
un dos iz dos.

00:23:10.748 --> 00:23:11.349
yo

00:23:54.409 --> 00:23:56.520
keyn shlekht vort gezogt

00:24:35.460 --> 00:24:37.052
kh'hob aykh gevolt vintshn

00:24:37.052 --> 00:24:39.656
az ir zolt zayn beyde gezunt un shtark

00:24:39.713 --> 00:24:42.303
un got tsu danken, ir hot kinder

00:24:39.780 --> 00:24:41.006
a sheynem dank aykh.

00:24:42.303 --> 00:24:46.377
gelungene kinder un eyniklekh, ir zolt hobn fun zey a sakh, a sakh nakhes

00:24:45.518 --> 00:24:47.706
a dank, a groysn dank aykh.

00:24:46.377 --> 00:24:49.352
un me zol keyn mol fun keyn tsores nisht visn.

00:24:53.922 --> 00:24:55.673
di mame heyst Rokhl

00:24:55.673 --> 00:24:59.740
un ikh Hodl, ⟨⟩ lebn ir, un dos iz mayn shvester Freytshe vos zi

00:24:59.740 --> 00:25:02.538
nor ikh bin geblibn lebn. mer keyner nisht geblibn lebn.

00:25:08.704 --> 00:25:11.988
dos bin ikh, di tsayt farn daytsh vos ikh hob gemakht a bild.

00:25:14.961 --> 00:25:20.865
dos bin ikh mit mayn man un mitn kind vos, mayn kind iz geboyrn gevorn in Daytshland.

00:25:22.862 --> 00:25:27.142
dos bin ikh nokhn bafrayung ven der rus hot bafrayt Lemberik.

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:32.813
dos bin ikh mit mayn zun in Daytshland.

00:25:35.991 --> 00:25:39.368
dos iz di mishpokhe fun mayn man, di shvester brider

00:25:39.368 --> 00:25:44.827
der zeyde mit der babn vos zey hobn ale umgekumen. bloyz mayn man iz geblibn lebn.

00:25:48.213 --> 00:25:51.999
dos bin ikh mit mayn man mit mayne kinder mit mayn shnur UNK

00:25:51.999 --> 00:25:53.425
der khasene

00:25:56.173 --> 00:26:00.234
dos iz mayn man mit mir mit mayne kinder, zun mit der tokhter.

00:26:03.565 --> 00:26:08.233
dos iz a bild fun der khasene fun mayn eynikl dem zun's tokhter.

00:26:12.205 --> 00:26:16.856
dos iz mayn tokhter mit tsvey kinder, mayne eyniklekh.

00:26:16.896 --> 00:26:19.235
Rokhele, RACHEL heyst zi.

00:26:22.026 --> 00:26:23.763
dos iz mayn tokhter

00:26:23.763 --> 00:26:25.714
fun di, far der khupe

00:26:25.714 --> 00:26:26.927
un dos iz mayn eydem

00:26:26.927 --> 00:26:28.599
un hintn zitsn tsvey

00:26:28.599 --> 00:26:30.960
meydelekh, dos UNK di meydelekh.

00:26:30.960 --> 00:26:32.173
di eyniklekh.

00:26:33.973 --> 00:26:38.050
dos bin ikh mit mayn man, mit dem ⟨dem⟩ man un finef eyniklekh.

00:26:43.852 --> 00:26:47.484
dos iz di tekhter fun mayn zun, mayne eyniklekh.

00:26:50.440 --> 00:26:53.174
do zenen mir geven in Ukrayne

00:26:53.174 --> 00:26:54.684
di shtot Ratne

00:26:54.684 --> 00:26:59.603
vos m'hot geshtelt a matseyve oyf man m- man's mishpokhe un ale yidn.
